<article class="article" id="article_13"><div class='article_title'>
Moving an application from Sinatra to Rails
</div>
<div class='article_content'><blockquote>
<p>I love both Sinatra and Rails, for different reasons. I&#39;ve heard a few different heuristics for which framework would be better for your application, but I&#39;m not sure the answer is all that simple, really. Regardless of which is correct for your application, I haven&#39;t seen a lot of people discussing how to move between the two frameworks.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>I&#39;ve done this move a few times now, so I wrote a blog post about the process you&#39;d take to <a href="http://blog.steveklabnik.com/posts/2012-01-17-moving-from-sinatra-to-rails">move a project from Sinatra to Rails</a>.</p>
